<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[باب الشين والدال]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[الشين والدال والراء]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">رشد:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">رَشَدَ الإِنسانُ يَرْشُدُ رُشْداً ورَشَاداً:</span> نَقِيْضُ الغَيِّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ورَشِدَ يَرْشَدُ رَشَداً:</span> نَقِيْضُ الضَّلالِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ويقولون <span class="c4">[/٢٣٦ ب]</span>: لا يَعْمى عليكَ الرُّشْدُ؛ إذا أرْشَدَكَ إنْسَانٌ إلى طَرِيْقٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ورَجُلٌ رَشِيْدٌ:</span> راشِدٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والإِرْشَادُ:</span> الدَّلالَةُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والرِّشْدَةُ:</span> نَقِيْضُ الغَيَّةِ، وُلِدَ لِرِشْدَةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">ويا رِشْدِيْنُ:</span> أي يا رَاشِدُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">والرَّشَدى:</span> الرُّشْدُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وقُرِئَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أهْدِكُمْ سَبِيْلَ الإِرْشَادِ»</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> من أرْشَدَه، وهي قِرَاءةٌ شاذَّةٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وكُلُّ ما ارْتَفَعَ عن الجِصِّ فهو:</span> رَشَادٌ.<span class="c5"> وكُلُّ صَخْرَةٍ:</span> رَشَادَةٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">شرد:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>شَرَدَ البَعِيرُ يَشْرُدُ شِرَاداً.<span class="c5"> وفَرَسٌ شَرُوْدٌ:</span> مُسْتَعْصٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) سورة غافر، آية رقم:٣٨، والقراءة المتداولة: (الرَّشادِ).</p> </div>